name: LaravelCP
tagline: A Laravel 4 based bootstrap admin interface
body:
### LaravelCP.
A modular control panel written in PHP using Laravel 4, jQuery 2, Bootstrap 3 & FontAwesome 4

```
$ cd your_repo_root/repo_name
$ git fetch origin
$ git checkout gh-pages
```

If you're using the GitHub for Mac, simply sync your repository and you'll see the new branch.

### Authors and Contributors
William Bowman (@gcphost) is the lead developer.

### Support or Contact
Contact William by posting an issue.
